## Limitations
The findings presented in this report are based on available literature and may not encompass all possible factors influencing belief in conspiracy theories. Additionally, the complexity of human psychology means that individual differences can lead to variations in susceptibility to conspiracy beliefs. Further research is needed to explore these nuances and the interplay between different influencing factors.

